    <abstract>
      <t>   This draft examines data transmission security in Industrial Internet
   identity resolution systems.  As pivotal infrastructure enabling
   secure cross-organizational sharing and intelligent correlation of
   heterogeneous data, these systems require robust security services
   during resolution processes.  The analysis focuses on essential
   protective measures for identity resolution operations.

	 </t>
